{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"05872372a6","title":"给刘雪节的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3a54aa68ae","index":0,"year":1938,"month":5,"day":28,"articleId":"05872372a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f27bf39f10","type":"paragraph","text":"给刘雪节的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"05872372a6"},{"id":"846dfadd67","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年5月28日）雪笔同志：收到了，谢谢！我已看了“座谈会记录”叫，很欢喜。如有新的，请续寄我。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"05872372a6"},{"id":"940eed5b7e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"05872372a6"},{"id":"fb28c11b77","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十八日[1]指刘雪笔给毛泽东的信和转交的《七月》杂志。刘雪（1912-1998）又名孙雪节，贵州郎（今属六查水市）人，文学评论家。当时在延安从事文艺工作。他在给毛泽东的信中说：“汉口《七月》半月刊主编胡风先生寄来第三集第一期《七月》，分赠一本给你，现特转上，析查收。[2]指《七月》华月刊在这期登载的题为《宣传、文学、旧形利用》的座谈会记录。参加这个座该会的有胡风、爱错督、吴组湘、欧阳凡海、鹿地巨、艾贵、吴具如、池田幸子。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"05872372a6"}],"page":{"id":"9fe5910380","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"05872372a6","start":217,"end":217}}}},"__N_SSG":true}